  "description": "If you're familiar with spinach and ricotta lasagne, you'll be sure to love this kale and feta version, which delivers way more on the flavour front! An 'open-lasagne' is both quicker and easier than traditional, as it's all done on the hob - lazy lasagne! Served with a sweet baby plum tomato and basil leaf salad. You can't get much feta than that!",
